outputs.output_descr: This project supports various activities geared towards ensuring effective national implementation of projects. It aims at strengthening national capacity for project implementation, in terms of results-based management, accurate and timely reporting, hereby facilitating project delivery.

project_descr: While assisting the Government in achieving its priorities and in line with the CPD (2012-2016), UNDP Jamaica is strategically supporting the achievement of inclusive and transformational outcomes within its areas of comparative advantage
